ka hoao ana o abela: He ʻano hoʻāʻo no ka hui ʻana o kahi moʻo pau ʻole
huikau loa: Ua ʻōlelo ʻia ka moʻo pau ʻole e hui pū ʻia inā pau ka huina o nā waiwai piha o nā hui.
ki\u02bbeki\u02bbe loa: ʻO ka waiwai kiʻekiʻe loa i loaʻa i kahi hana
palena iki loa: ʻO ka waiwai haʻahaʻa i loaʻa i kahi hana
waiwai piha: ʻO ka waiwai maikaʻi ʻole o kahi helu maoli me ka nānā ʻole i kona hōʻailona
kaha ho\u02bbololi: He moʻo pau ʻole nona nā huaʻōlelo ma waena o ka maikaʻi a me ka maikaʻi ʻole
ho\u02bb\u0101\u02bbo p\u016b\u02bbali \: ʻO ke ala i hoʻohana ʻia no ka hōʻoia ʻana he moʻo convergent ka moʻo ʻokoʻa me nā huaʻōlelo e emi ana ka waiwai paʻa
annulus: He mea apo apo, he wahi i paa i na poai concentric elua
antiderivative: He hana hoʻokaʻawale i like kona derivative me ka hana kumu
asymptote: ʻO kahi laina e pili ana ka mamao ma waena o ka pihi a me ka laina i ka ʻole me ka hoʻokahi a i ʻole ʻelua o nā hoʻonohonoho x a i ʻole y e pili ana i ka palena ʻole.
\u02bb\u0101pana ma lalo o kahi \u02bb\u: ʻO ka mea hoʻohui e hōʻike ana i ka ʻāpana ma waena o ka piʻi y=f(x), ke axis-x, a me nā laina kū pololei x=a a me x=b, kahi a a me b nā palena o ka hoʻohui.
lula kaulahao: ʻO ka derivative o ka hana hoʻohui ʻia ka derivative o ka hana o waho i loiloi ʻia i ka hana o loko ka manawa o ka derivative o ka hana i loko.
helu \u02bboko\u02bba: E aʻo ana i ka wikiwiki o ka hoʻololi ʻana o nā nui. Hoʻohana ʻia ka hoʻohālikelike derivative e wehewehe i ka wikiwiki o ka hoʻololi ʻana o kahi hana
ho\u02bbololi k\u016b\u02bboko\u02bba: He nui i hana ʻia i loko o ka hana a i ʻole ka hoʻohālikelike, e hōʻike pinepine ana i ke kumu i loko o kahi pilina kumu-a-hopena.
ho\u02bbololi hilina\u02bbi: ʻO ka hopena a i ʻole ka hopena i ka hana a i ʻole ka pilina e loli ana ma muli o nā waiwai o nā nui ʻē aʻe
k\u0101\u02bbei kapu: Hōʻike i nā waiwai kūpono a pau i hiki ke hoʻohana ʻia i mea hoʻokomo i kahi hana
laula: ʻO ka hoʻonohonoho o nā mea hiki ke hana i kahi hana
palena: ʻO kahi manaʻo e wehewehe ana i nā waiwai hoʻopuka e hoʻokokoke aku ai i ka wā e hoʻokokoke ai nā mea hoʻokomo i kekahi waiwai
n\u0101 mea ho\u02bbopuka: He manaʻo e ana i ka wikiwiki o ka hoʻololi ʻana a i ʻole ka piʻi o ka laina tangent ma kekahi wahi ma kahi hana.
helu ho\u02bbohui: ʻO ka hoʻolōʻihi ʻia o ka helu helu e pili ana i ka ʻimi ʻana i ka antiderivative o kahi hana i hāʻawi ʻia ka derivative
ho\u02bbohui laina: ʻO ka hoʻohui ʻana o kahi hana ma ka laina o ka pihi
ho\u02bbohui honua: ʻO ka hoʻonui ʻana i nā mea hoʻohui like ʻole i ka hoʻohui ʻana ma luna o nā ʻili
helu helu lehulehu: ʻO ka hoʻonui ʻia ʻana o ka helu helu ma ka helu hoʻokahi i ka helu helu me nā hana o nā ʻano like ʻole
kahua vector: He kiko ma ka lewa nona ka nui a me ke kuhikuhi
helu helu vector: He hoʻonui ʻia o ka helu helu e pili ana i ka ʻokoʻa a me ka hoʻohui ʻana o ke kahua vector i ka hakahaka Euclidean ʻekolu.
hiki i ka vector: ʻO ke kahua vector e hoʻāla ai i kahi kahua solenoidal ma o ka curl operator
